divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving up the Norweigin Grade towards Thousand Oaks. Blinking lights made me first notice the object. I lost sight of the object when I continued up the grade. When I got to Thousand Oaks, it was further east than it had been. It was not a plane...too large.
